snippet.title: PATHOGEN X - DEMO END TRAILER
snippet.description:
Announcement of the release of the demo version in steam

Release date 04.04.2024

Do not miss the opportunity to try out the game one of the first, the demo version will be available in a short period of time, until the release of the full game!
